      "date": "2013-04-07 10:59:04.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/b8be8f6a-9f6f-11e2-86dc-52540035b04c).  Ran 14 tests.  No failures.",
